<p><strong>Fixed</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/TRowbotham">@TRowbotham</a> fixed the unprefixed gradient detect to cover newer gradient syntaxes - <a href="https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/pull/1621">#1621</a></li>
