<li><a href="https://github.com/jorrit">@jorrit</a> fixed a typo - <a href="https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/pull/1708">#1708</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/roblarsen">@roblarsen</a> added a hasOwnProperty check to the Modernizr class name creation process to avoid extraneous classes - <a href="https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/pull/1709">#1709</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/aFarkas">@aFarkas</a> fixed the <code>sizes</code> detect (used in responsive images) for Safari 9 - <a href="https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/pull/1728">#1728</a></li>
</ul>
