<li>updating <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/marked">marked</a> to v0.2.10 to v3.5.0, which actually fixes <a href="https://app.snyk.io/vuln/npm:marked:20140131">several</a> <a href="https://app.snyk.io/vuln/npm:marked:20140131-1">code</a> <a href="https://app.snyk.io/vuln/npm:marked:20140131-2">vulnerabilities</a></li>
</ul>
]]></description><link>https://modernizr.com/news//news/modernizr-3-2-0</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://modernizr.com/news//news/modernizr-3-2-0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[<a href="https://twitter.com/patrickkettner">Patrick Kettner</a>]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 28 Oct 2015 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title><![CDATA[Modernizr 3.1.0]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>We promised faster releases - and here they are. Modernizr 3.1.0 is a pretty small release, but none the less useful.</p>
