<li><a href="https://github.com/patrickkettner">@patrickkettner</a> added the <a href="https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/blob/feb841be8501dddffeaf37ef17bef1fbadb72d5d/src/prefixedCSSValue.js"><code>prefixedCSSValue</code> utility function</a>, as a way to check for prefixed versions of CSS values - <a href="https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/commit/6bd55c">6bd55c</a></li>
